title: A weekly summary of all the songs played on 'Battle of The Blades.' | CBC Television
text:
Week two - September 26, 2019



Kygo & Whitney Houston - Higher Love

Natalie Spooner and Andrew Poje dance to "Higher Love" by Kygo & Whitney Houston on week two of Battle of the Blades.

Natalie Spooner and Andrew Poje dance to Higher Love by Whitney Houston/Kygo. 1:45 Natalie Spooner and Andrew Poje dance to "Higher Love" by Kygo & Whitney Houston on week two of Battle of the Blades.
